{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回\"九阴假经\"：欧阳锋叔侄胁迫郭靖默写九阴真经，郭靖拒绝，洪七公突袭救出郭靖。欧阳锋放毒蛇围攻，师徒二人被困桅杆，靠郭靖身上药气驱蛇。白雕传信黄蓉。洪七公设假经之计，让郭靖将经文颠倒黑白写成九阴假经交给欧阳锋。洪七公偷酒时发现欧阳锋欲烧船灭口，师徒乘小艇逃离。黄蓉驾轻舟赶到，跃上大船却被欧阳锋挟持。洪七公与欧阳锋在烈焰中激斗，郭靖在小艇上以左右互搏术折断欧阳克臂骨，救出黄蓉。大船烧断沉没，洪七公饶过欧阳锋，让他带着假经离去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老叫化可从来没享过这个福。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怕什么？还能吃了你么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请两位爷胡乱用些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们出去罢，老叫化见了美貌的娘儿们吃不下饭。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "别吃的好，老毒物鬼计多端，只吃白饭无碍。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "不知他要周大哥做什么事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "决不能是好事。这一下老顽童一定大大不妙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "周老爷子请郭爷到后舱说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "白衣少女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭爷到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "周大哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "老顽童跟我打赌输了，我叫他做事，他却不肯。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "嗯？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "我叫他把九阴真经默写出来给我瞧瞧，那老顽童竟说话不算数。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "周大哥呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "他曾言道，若不愿依我的话办事，就跳在大海里喂鲨鱼。哼，总算他也是个响当当的人物，这句话倒没赖。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他⋯⋯他⋯⋯",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "当今之世，只有你知道真经全文，快写下来罢。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你和老叫化刚才所吃的酒菜之中，都已下了毒药，若不服我叔父的独门解药，六个时辰后毒性发作，就像海里的那些鲨鱼般死了。只要你好好写出来，自然饶了你师徒二人性命。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你已把经文牢牢记在心中，写了出来，于你丝毫无损，又有什么迟疑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "你害了我义兄性命，我跟你仇深似海！你要杀便杀，想要我屈从，那叫做痴心妄想！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "好小子，倒有骨气！你不怕死，连你师父性命也不救么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "老毒物，你千方百计要占我上风，老天爷总是不许！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "七兄，又要来伸量兄弟的功夫么？咱们到了岸上再打不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "你跟我徒儿这般亲热干什么？拉着他的手不放。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "我跟老顽童赌赛，是我赢了不是？你是中证不是？老顽童不守约言，我只唯你是问，可不是？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "那不错。老顽童呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "周大哥给他⋯⋯给他逼着跳海死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老毒物，你逼死老顽童，自有全真教道士跟你算帐。你武功再强，也未必挡得住全真七子围攻。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "那时你这中证可也脱不了干系。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "好啊，到时候我打狗棒棒打落水狗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "郭贤侄，你功夫还差得远呢！人家这么一伸手，你就听人摆布。去跟师父练上十年，再出来闯江湖罢。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "臭叫化，明天这时刻，你身上毒发，就要在我跟前爬着叫救命啦。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老贼厮鸟要凿沉了船。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "快抢船后的小舢舨。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老毒物用蛇攻！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老毒物给我这许多练功的靶子，真再好也没有。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "妙极，妙极！老毒物，你连我小徒儿也打不过，还逞什么英雄豪强？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "快上桅杆。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "我打死他侄儿，给周大哥报仇。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "蛇！蛇！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好呀，咱们耗上啦。转舵向东！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖儿，淋尿给直娘贼喝个饱。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请啊，请啊！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快撤蛇阵！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "手下",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "洪帮主、郭小爷，欧阳老爷整治了上等酒席，请两位下来饮用。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你叫欧阳锋来，咱们请他吃尿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "但教我那个女徒儿在此，她聪明伶俐，定有对付老毒物的法子。咱爷儿俩可只有干瞪眼、流馋涎的份儿。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "师父，莫非蓉儿也乘了船出来？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "那妙极了。只可惜雕儿太小，负不起咱师徒二人。咱们困在这里无计可施，你快叫她来作个计较。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "老叫化最爱的就是吃喝，老毒物偏生瞄准了来折磨人。我一生只练外功，抵御酒菜的定力可就差了点儿。靖儿，咱们下去打他个落花流水再上来，好不好？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "白雕既已带了信去，情势必能有变。您老人家且再等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "天下味道最不好的东西，你道是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "我不知道，是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "有一次我到极北苦寒之地，大雪中饿了八天，松鼠固然找不到，到后来连树皮也寻不着了。我在雪地泥中乱挖乱掘，忽然掘到了五条活的东西，老叫化幸亏这五条东西救了一命，多挨了一天。第二日就打到了一只黄狼，饱啖了一顿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "那五条东西是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "是蚯蚓，肥得很。生吞下肚，不敢咬嚼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "靖儿，现下若有蚯蚓，我也吃了，但有一件最脏最臭之物，老叫化宁可吃自己的脚趾头，却也不肯吃它，你道是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "我知道啦，是臭屎！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "我对你说，天下最脏的东西，是西毒欧阳锋身上的烂肉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对，对！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "洪伯父、郭世兄，家叔但求郭世兄写出九阴真经来一观，别无他意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "直娘贼，就是不安好心！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "小贼种，老子中了你狗叔父的诡计，认输便了。快拿酒肉来吃，明天再说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "这次酒菜里没毒么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "傻小子，那厮鸟要你写经与他，怎能害你性命？快吃得饱饱地，咱们另有计较。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "老毒物要九阴真经，你写一部九阴假经与他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "九阴假经？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "是啊。九阴真经到底是怎样，你爱怎么写就怎么写，黄药师手中虽有真经，也决不会借给他去核对真假。下卷的头上几句他侄儿背过，你别写错。他见头上的不错，以为后面的也必不错，你偏偏将后面的经文乱改一气，教他照着练功，那就练一百年也只练成个屁！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "欧阳锋武学湛深，又机警狡猾，弟子胡书乱写，必定让他识破，这便如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你可要写得似是而非，三句真话，夹半句假话，逢到练功的秘诀，却给他增增减减，经上说一的，你给他改成九，说九的改成一，二变八，三变七，四变六，五变十，倒转来也照改，老毒物再机灵，也决不能瞧出来。我宁可七日七夜不饮酒不吃饭，也要瞧瞧他老毒物练九阴假经的模样。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "他若照着假经练功，不但虚耗时日，劳而无功，只怕反而身子受害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你快好好想一下如何窜改，只要他起了丝毫疑心，那就大事不成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "那下卷经文的前几页，欧阳克这小畜生在桃花岛上读了或许还记得，那就不可多改。然而稍稍加上几个错字，谅那小畜生也分辨不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "老叫化武功自成一家，九阴真经就放在面前，也不屑瞧它一眼。只有不成材的厮鸟，自己功夫不成，才巴巴的想偷什么真金真银，王重阳与黄药师当年得了真经，又何尝去练经中功夫？做人有没出息，是不是英雄好汉，分别就在于此。对你狗叔父说，真经就写与他，叫他去闭门苦练，练成后再来跟老叫化打架。真经自然是好东西，可是我就偏偏不放在眼里。瞧他得了真经，能不能奈何得了老叫化。他去苦练九阴真经上的武功，本门功夫自然便荒废了，一加一减，到头来还不是跟老叫化半斤八两？这叫作脱裤子放屁，多此一举。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "洪伯父此言错矣！家叔武功已至化境，洪伯父如此本领，却也赢不了家叔一招半式，他又何必再学九阴真经？家叔常对小侄言道，他深信九阴真经浪得虚名，哗众欺人，否则王重阳当年得了九阴真经，为什么又不见有什么惊世骇俗的武功显示出来？家叔发愿要指出经中的虚妄浮夸之处，好教天下武学之士尽皆知晓，这真经有名无实，谬误极多，不必拚了命去争夺。这岂非造福武林的一件盛举么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "你瞎吹什么牛皮！靖儿，把经文默写给他瞧。倘若老毒物真能指得出九阴真经中有一两个错处，老叫化给他磕头。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "经已写完，大功告成。各处舱里的油柴硫磺都安排齐备了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 435,
      "line_end": 435
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "都齐备了，只要一引火，这艘大船转眼就化灰烬，这次可要把臭叫化烤焦啦。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 437,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "咱们再等片刻，待那姓郭的小子睡熟了，你先下小艇去，千万小心，别让老叫化知觉。我到这里来点火。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 439,
      "line_end": 439
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "那些姬人和蛇夫怎么安排？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "臭叫化是一代武学大宗师，总得有些人殉葬，才合他身分。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 443,
      "line_end": 443
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "叔叔，再过一个时辰，那姓郭的小子葬身海底，世上知晓九阴真经的，就只你老人家一个啦。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "不，有两个。难道我不传你么？还有个黄药师，也知真经，咱们日后想个什么法儿，俟机送他归天。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 453
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "叔叔，咱们去把经文用油纸、油布包好，外面再熔了白蜡浇上，免得让海水浸坏了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 455,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好酒啊好酒！再来十壶！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 461
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老毒物，你我再拆一千招，分个高下。唔，唔，好小子，行行！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你跟着我行事，别问原因。现下悄悄出去，别让人瞧见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "上小艇去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "割断绳索。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 495,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咦，那是什么船？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 505,
      "line_end": 505
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "郭靖呢？你把他怎么了？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快上那船！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "火，火！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "不错，老毒物放火烧船，要烧死咱爷儿俩！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "快去救蓉儿。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "划近去！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_huang_rong",
      "text": "蓉儿，我和靖儿都在这儿，游水过来！游过来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放开我！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 541
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "臭叫化，黄姑娘在我这里，你瞧见了么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "他以此要挟，想上咱们小艇，哼！我去夺蓉儿回来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 549,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "我也去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 551,
      "line_end": 551
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "不，你守着小艇，莫让老毒物夺去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 553,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 555,
      "line_end": 555
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "text": "臭叫化，你待怎地？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 559,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "来来，再拆一千招。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 561,
      "line_end": 561
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "老毒物好不要脸，快把她放下艇去，我跟你在这里决个胜负。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 565
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "你们先下小艇！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "放手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳克",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "你一动，我就一掌劈碎她脑袋。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 605,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_ke",
      "text": "蓉儿，你瞧那西毒好凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 597,
      "line_end": 597
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": "char_huang_rong",
      "text": "我去请师父下来，好不好？那船转眼要沉啦。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 599
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_rong",
      "speaker_name": "黄蓉",
      "listener": "char_guo_jing",
      "text": "快去帮师父！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 631,
      "line_end": 631
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳锋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慢着，现下我身上也湿了，咱俩公公平平的决个胜败。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_qi_gong",
      "speaker_name": "洪七公",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_feng",
      "text": "妙极，妙极！今日这一战打得当真痛快。",
